{"data":[{"id":564035770,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"c41530803720c944ee8292911b8750bb","url_token":"dnchfnu-nffn","name":"always","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-459a8250c78f918b1bc99609b19c254b_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-459a8250c78f918b1bc99609b19c254b_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/c41530803720c944ee8292911b8750bb","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":1,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/564035770","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c4c7885093522689a7829db949cf731c_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546323406,"updated_time":1546323406,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":6,"comment_count":0,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e证明有点胡搅蛮缠。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e大致可以了解他的基本思路，不就分了三部分嘛，二三四页证明充分运用了第一页的结论，这里就光说说第一页证明的问题。按照他的定义（负质数当作质数的相反数）：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eA＝{x|x＝±p±q,p,q为质数,x∈2n,n∈Z}\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eB＝{x|x＝p+q,p,q为质数,x∈2n,n∈N+}\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e易得B为A的子集。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e暂且不说这个无聊诡异的负质数定义和对于-1的处理，就算这样可以，光看他的证明。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e第一个问题，如下图：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f6ed01d65e7bf5cf0aedca67d58fcd74_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"865\" data-rawheight=\"257\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-433eaf9d9c95e81a3cbe6197606089f7_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"865\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f6ed01d65e7bf5cf0aedca67d58fcd74_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='865'%20height='257'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"865\" data-rawheight=\"257\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-433eaf9d9c95e81a3cbe6197606089f7_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"865\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f6ed01d65e7bf5cf0aedca67d58fcd74_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f6ed01d65e7bf5cf0aedca67d58fcd74_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e很好，你假设-1是一个质数，可是谁告诉你2n+1也是质数，2n怎么能说是属于集合A呢？不过，也有可能作者笔误太多，思维太精奇，常人无法看懂罢了，我们姑且认为这是对的，暂且放下不谈。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e接下来，敲黑板，重点来了。第二个问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-ae58d68bba26d6b357d7f2ce94842f91_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1135\" data-rawheight=\"366\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-a5db4b45fdc1ea04e4d62f96ff744983_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1135\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-ae58d68bba26d6b357d7f2ce94842f91_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1135'%20height='366'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1135\" data-rawheight=\"366\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-a5db4b45fdc1ea04e4d62f96ff744983_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1135\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-ae58d68bba26d6b357d7f2ce94842f91_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-ae58d68bba26d6b357d7f2ce94842f91_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e原命题被变为逆否命题，好，可以。我们简要说一下逆否命题的核心：有一个正偶数，它不属于集合A。哥德巴赫猜想说：任意一个大于2的正偶数可分为两个质数之和，我们现在基本认为这是正确的（虽然不会证明），所以可以说：任意一个大于2的偶数都属于集合B，又因为B是A的子集，所以任意一个大于2的偶数都属于集合A。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e证明人提的反例是让这个偶数为2。但是他忘了：2=5+（-3），按照负质数的定义，2属于集合A，则该命题错误，原命题也不成立，无法证明猜想。但证明人在如图第二行的证明中称2不属于A，这是一个最大的纰漏，没有任何挽回余地，它导致了之后的证明也完全错误。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e第三个问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我们说说他奇怪的证明思路。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e先提出一个命题：若a为真，则b，我们通过一系列证明可知a为假，所以若a为真，则b。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这是什么鬼？？？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e第四个问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e后面的东西完！全！看！不！懂！（恕在下才疏学浅）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e为什么1+1和-1+（6n+3）是并立的关系（刚开始证明也用了或），如果这也可以“或”，我能给你“或”无数种，让你没法证明。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e总的来说，这篇证明，引入了几个无聊的新定义，证了一大堆充满纰漏，令人不懂的结论（还有好多没法用“看不懂”来挽回的无比明显的错误），大约这仁兄的确是个中二民科吧。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"证明有点胡搅蛮缠。大致可以了解他的基本思路，不就分了三部分嘛，二三四页证明充分运用了第一页的结论，这里就光说说第一页证明的问题。按照他的定义（负质数当作质数的相反数）：A＝{x|x＝±p±q,p,q为质数,x∈2n,n∈Z}B＝{x|x＝p+q,p,q为质数,x∈2n,n∈N…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationshi